In the MATTER OF the Suspension or Revocation of the License of Amgad HESSEIN, M.D. License No.: 25MA067650 To Practice Medicine and Surgery in the State of New Jersey. (Amgad A. Hessein - Petitioner) C-854 September Term 2018
081999 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003308-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
